      <p class="prompt">$ whoami</p>
      <p>Backend Systems Engineer | Performance Optimization | Infrastructure</p>
      <p class="prompt">$ cat ./bio.txt</p>
      <p>
        Building high-performance systems and scalable infrastructure. 
        Focused on distributed systems, optimization, and clean architecture.
      </p>
      <p class="prompt">$ ls -la ~/skills/</p>
      <p>{stats.topLanguages.join(' â€¢ ') || 'Loading...'}</p>
